Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live as you please, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the flow of time, as a result of\Nvarious circumstances and strong spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people come to question the world they live in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day we meet will come at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The judicial island Enies Lobby is the front door
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that leads to the World Government,\Na huge organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they've caused it to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,neither the Navy nor pirates\Nwill leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that the Straw Hats\Nare now known all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so is this wanted poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this incredible?!\NIt's the spitting image of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He pulled one crazy stunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! It's an article on Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he toppled the Tower of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His bounty is going to skyrocket after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enies Lobby is famous\Nfor Water Seven's sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't that far from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:04:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For them to be within range...\NWhat a pitiable, unfortunate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Get ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to get busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back three days before the\Nworld was shocked and amazed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Straw Hat Pirates' wanted posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was an event that\Noccurred on a certain island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Banaro Island on the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Most Heinous Power!\NBlackbeard's Darkness Attacks Ace"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ace! Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "Commander" after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That word is meant to be\Nreserved for people you respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you must be "Fire Fist" Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's me. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... you've already become\Na great captain in your own right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Captain Marshall D. Teach\Nof the Blackbeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Ace! I haven't seen you in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the deal?\NHow'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach, let's cut the idle talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know the rules, having lived\Nthrough twice as much as others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me say something first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, Ace?\NWhy don't you join my crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize the world with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already planned out how\NI'm going to rise up in power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard's reign is over!\NI'll become the next Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I'm gonna kill\NStraw Hat Luffy, who is in Water Seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a gift to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.89,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another reason I can't let you go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And naturally, there is no way I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...join your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:07:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of your men could use a lesson in manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Commandment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Auger, Burgess! Keep outta this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't stand a chance\Nagainst that man. Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sorry!\N--Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain!\N--Aw, that burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:08:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, men! Give me some space!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, Ace. You're burning\Nto kill me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no surprise. Murdering a\Ncrewmate is a grievous crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I killed the\N4th division commander Thatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have a choice! He got his hands on\Nthe Devil Fruit that I had my sights set on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's rule dictated that whoever\Nfound the fruit could eat it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I memorized what every fruit\Nin the book looked like,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I knew it was the one I'd been\Nlooking for the second I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I spent all those\Ndecades on Whitebeard's ship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was because I figured that was\Nthe most likely place to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woulda given up if fortune\Nhadn't smiled down on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that fruit fell into my friend's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:10:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you killed Thatch and stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how the ball bounces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ability chose me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has made me the most\Npowerful person out there, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's rare, even for a Logia type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, isn't your body made out of fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's the same black smoke from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those pirates are still in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still going at it?\NIf they destroy any more of our village...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep away from them!\NOur only option is to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Commander Ace. You can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that this is the most\Nevil power in Devil Fruit history.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Logia Devil Fruit, Dark-Dark Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a man made of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a taste of just how powerful it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is about to cut loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry away from here,\Nwe'll get caught in the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness gushing from his body\Nis crawling across the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy! It's pitch black, almost like\Nthere is a hole in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary how it feels like it could absorb you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get away!\NGet as far away as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go through the forest!\NRun all the way to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness is gravity!\NIt has the power to pull everything in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a ray of light can\Nescape from its infinite gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're up against me...\Nand I'm still untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going after you just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay there and\Nenjoy the view of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground is devouring the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark gravity uses its limitless power\Nto condense objects and crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a nightmare? Our village is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'll show you what\Nhappened to the missing village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold the shambled mess it has become!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liberation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our village... has been reduced to rubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you get it, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power I've obtained!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiery Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I fully understand how great\Nthe power of darkness is.\N--Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But here's what puzzles me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--If it's a Logia, these attacks\Nshould go right through you.\N--Dang, this is hot! Hot, hot, hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you:\NDarkness draws everything in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including bullets, swords,\Npunches, fire, and lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the rest of you, I don't get the\Noption of letting stuff pass through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels far worse pain than the\Naverage person in every way possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange for accepting that risk,\Nthere is one other thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I am able to absorb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be exact, dark gravity has the ability
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to draw in a Devil Fruit\Npower holder's physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Have you figured it out, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's been a while since someone's\Nlanded a punch on you, eh, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that you got it when I grabbed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another thing that my darkness drags in is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that while I'm touching them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fruit power holders\Ncan't use any of their powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Logia, Zoan, and Paramythia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against a world of Devil Fruit power holders\Nwho are overconfident in their abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've obtained a means of attack\Nthat cannot be defended against!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just can't let you catch me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already proved that you can't\Nescape from my dark gravity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St. Elmo's Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! The fire lances...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He messed up some vertebrae!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His new power is a pain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cross Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.89,0:19:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banana Rock...! It's collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? They can't be humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the village! What is going\Nto happen... to our whole island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had assumed that Devil Fruit power holders\Nwere so preoccupied with their powers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they would be pushovers\Nonce they lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I should have expected one\Nof Whitebeard's commanders
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:20:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be a fearsome fighter\Nin basic combat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, today brings us\Nto another crossroad of fates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is rendered\Npowerless before darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone as powerful as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this makes me want\Nyour power all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I yield to power, there's no\Npoint in being born a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never leave anything to\Nbe regretted later in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you live like that in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.04,0:21:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Commandment...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun or the darkness--\Nthere'll be only one winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make Whitebeard the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Decisive Battle of Banaro Island"\Non the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight between these two pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be described as the trigger for a\Nmassive incident that is soon to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're hitting the sea of adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head straight for Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no! With the New World nearby,\Nwe should exercise caution!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sanji! There's a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.77,0:22:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's missing both a sail and an ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sailing full-speed\Ntoward trouble already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Mysterious Band of Pirates!\NSunny and the Dangerous Trap"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
